https://specificity.keegan.st/

The below site is used to select the colors 

https://coolors.co/

Tools --> contrast-checker --> To check the score for the text color and background color

The below site we can use to check whether the css is supported in this browser
and how we can use that css in that browser

https://caniuse.com/

